{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Baekjoon-1002/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Technical blog by Gatsby"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"47733d20-1722-5f0a-a7b3-763d83906679","excerpt":"백준 알고리즘 (Java) 1002-터렛 1. 문제 설명  https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/1002 2. 접근 방법 문제 파악 한 좌표에서 r만큼 떨어진 점들의 집합 => 원 조규현 기준으로 류재명이 있을 수 있는 좌표의 집합 => 중심이 (x1, y…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>백준 알고리즘 (Java)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>1002-터렛</h2>\n<h3>1. 문제 설명</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0adfac95763729eb8e2c5d0427e244ba/41045/baekjoon-1002.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 95.56962025316456%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"baekjoon 1002\"\n        title=\"baekjoon 1002\"\n        src=\"/static/0adfac95763729eb8e2c5d0427e244ba/f058b/baekjoon-1002.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0adfac95763729eb8e2c5d0427e244ba/c26ae/baekjoon-1002.png 158w,\n/static/0adfac95763729eb8e2c5d0427e244ba/6bdcf/baekjoon-1002.png 315w,\n/static/0adfac95763729eb8e2c5d0427e244ba/f058b/baekjoon-1002.png 630w,\n/static/0adfac95763729eb8e2c5d0427e244ba/40601/baekjoon-1002.png 945w,\n/static/0adfac95763729eb8e2c5d0427e244ba/78612/baekjoon-1002.png 1260w,\n/static/0adfac95763729eb8e2c5d0427e244ba/41045/baekjoon-1002.png 2434w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/1002\">https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/1002</a></p>\n<h3>2. 접근 방법</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>문제 파악</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>한 좌표에서 r만큼 떨어진 점들의 집합 => 원</li>\n<li>조규현 기준으로 류재명이 있을 수 있는 좌표의 집합 => 중심이 (x1, y1)이고 반지름의 길이가 r1인 원</li>\n<li>백승환 기준으로 류재명이 있을 수 있는 좌표의 집합 => 중심이 (x2, y2)이고 반지름의 길이가 r2인 원</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>사용할 알고리즘</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>가능한 모든 경우를 그려본 후 경우에 따라 케이스를 분리한다.</li>\n<li>기하학, 수학, 구현</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>3. 문제 풀이</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>dist는 두 원 사이의 거리로 정의한다. (<code class=\"language-text\">Math.sqrt(Math.pow(x2 - x1, 2) + Math.pow(y2 - y1, 2))</code>)</li>\n<li>\n<p>두 원이 동일할 때 (원의 중심과 반지름의 길이 모두 같을 때)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>두 원일 동일할 경우 류재명이 있을 수 있는 점들의 집합은 두 원과 같다. (무한대의 경우이다)</li>\n<li>두 원의 중심과 반지름의 길이가 모두 같은 경우 (<code class=\"language-text\">x1 == x2 &amp;&amp; y1 == y2 &amp;&amp; r1 == r2</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>두 원이 만나지 않을 때</p>\n<ul>\n<li>두 원이 만나지 않을 경우 류재명이 있을 수 있는 점들의 집합은 공집합이다. (있을 수 있는 경우가 존재하지 않는다)</li>\n<li>\n<p>두 원이 만나지 않는 경우는 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>두 원이 멀리 떨어져 있는 경우 (<code class=\"language-text\">dist &gt; r1 + r2</code>)\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/24203f847bf2beaca3576766cfeb197f/889a4/not_meet_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.56962025316456%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"not meet 1\"\n        title=\"not meet 1\"\n        src=\"/static/24203f847bf2beaca3576766cfeb197f/f058b/not_meet_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/24203f847bf2beaca3576766cfeb197f/c26ae/not_meet_1.png 158w,\n/static/24203f847bf2beaca3576766cfeb197f/6bdcf/not_meet_1.png 315w,\n/static/24203f847bf2beaca3576766cfeb197f/f058b/not_meet_1.png 630w,\n/static/24203f847bf2beaca3576766cfeb197f/889a4/not_meet_1.png 658w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>한 원이 다른 하나의 원 안에 있는 경우 (<code class=\"language-text\">dist + r1 &lt; r2 || dist + r2 &lt; r1</code>)\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/65e3ae2afac0af494e57bace2b8c7335/c5bb3/not_meet_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"not meet 2\"\n        title=\"not meet 2\"\n        src=\"/static/65e3ae2afac0af494e57bace2b8c7335/f058b/not_meet_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/65e3ae2afac0af494e57bace2b8c7335/c26ae/not_meet_2.png 158w,\n/static/65e3ae2afac0af494e57bace2b8c7335/6bdcf/not_meet_2.png 315w,\n/static/65e3ae2afac0af494e57bace2b8c7335/f058b/not_meet_2.png 630w,\n/static/65e3ae2afac0af494e57bace2b8c7335/c5bb3/not_meet_2.png 680w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>두 원이 한 접점에서 만날 때</p>\n<ul>\n<li>두 원이 한 접점에서 만날 경우 류재명이 있을 수 있는 점은 하나이다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>두 원이 한 점에서 만나는 경우는 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>한 원이 다른 원의 외부에서 접하는 경우 (<code class=\"language-text\">dist == r1 + r2</code>)\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 566px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1044c875a00a48b8243472844ab0401b/6fe44/one_meet_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.53164556962025%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"one meet 1\"\n        title=\"one meet 1\"\n        src=\"/static/1044c875a00a48b8243472844ab0401b/6fe44/one_meet_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1044c875a00a48b8243472844ab0401b/c26ae/one_meet_1.png 158w,\n/static/1044c875a00a48b8243472844ab0401b/6bdcf/one_meet_1.png 315w,\n/static/1044c875a00a48b8243472844ab0401b/6fe44/one_meet_1.png 566w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>한 원이 다른 원의 내부에서 접하는 경우 (<code class=\"language-text\">dist + r1 == r2 || dist + r2 == r1</code>)\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 306px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5130a94fcbf6477b21d72ee0346400d6/98b92/one_meet_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 101.8987341772152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"one meet 2\"\n        title=\"one meet 2\"\n        src=\"/static/5130a94fcbf6477b21d72ee0346400d6/98b92/one_meet_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5130a94fcbf6477b21d72ee0346400d6/c26ae/one_meet_2.png 158w,\n/static/5130a94fcbf6477b21d72ee0346400d6/98b92/one_meet_2.png 306w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>그 외</p>\n<ul>\n<li>그 외에는 두 원이 두 접점에서 만난다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>위의 경우를 코드로 표현하면 아래와 같다.</p>\n<h3>4. 코드</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>io<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">BufferedReader</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>io<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">IOException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>io<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">InputStreamReader</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">java<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>util<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">StringTokenizer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Main</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> args<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">throws</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NumberFormatException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">IOException</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">BufferedReader</span> br <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BufferedReader</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">InputStreamReader</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>in<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">T</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>br<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">readLine</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token class-name\">StringTokenizer</span> line <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">StringTokenizer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>br<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">readLine</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> x1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>line<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">nextToken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> y1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>line<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">nextToken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> r1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>line<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">nextToken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> x2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>line<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">nextToken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> y2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>line<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">nextToken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> r2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>line<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">nextToken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Distance between (x1, y1) and (x2, y2)</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">double</span> dist <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sqrt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x2 <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> x1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>y2 <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> y1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Case infinite => two circles are same</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x1 <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> x2 <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> y1 <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> y2 <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> r1 <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> r2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Case 0 => two circles are never meet</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dist <span class=\"token operator\">></span> r1 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> r2 <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dist <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> r1 <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> r2 <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> dist <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> r2 <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> r1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Case 1 => two circles meet only one dot(접하는 경우)</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dist <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> r1 <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> r2 <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> dist <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> r2 <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> r1 <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> dist <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> r1 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> r